{"tid":765694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國學者節目上批習近平  期間被消失過程全程被錄下","createTime":"2018-08-03T03:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T05:22:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"21d243c87738a4530a29b3d3824eb14b2d2e0af0","tid":765694,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:53:29.000Z","msg":"中國國家主席習近平的非洲政策，近來遭到一名國內學者公開抨擊，說他在進行「灑錢外交」，而這名發公開信給習近平的山東大學退休教授，1日在與美國之音一個政論節目進行電話連線時，警方當場破門闖入他家將人強行帶走，而整個節目也全程轉播了這名教授「被消失」的恐怖過程。<br />\n<br />\n「我有我的言論自由」，這是中國山東大學退休教授孫文廣，1日接受美國之音的電話連線時，被公安強行帶走前的最後一句呼喊。<br />\n<br />\n其實孫文廣先前就曾發表公開信，表示中國有大量貧困人口，也有各種問題亟待解決，呼籲習近平不要去國外做灑錢外交。這段電話連線的一開始，他就提及自己因為這封信，被警方加強監視。<br />\n<br />\n高齡已84歲的孫文廣表示，他當時是手持菜刀，拼了老命和警方一邊對峙，一邊進行電話連線，而這整段連線過程其實短短不到10分鐘，到了第7分鐘的時候，就疑似遭8名公安強行帶走。<br />\n<br />\n之後節目製作單位試圖聯繫孫文廣，但一直沒有回音，中國外交部新聞司方面，對此也沒有任何回應，雖然過去中國民眾發表批評當局言論後，疑似「被消失」的事件屢見不鮮，但這回在電話連線進行中，在直播的狀況之下疑似被強行帶走，卻非同小可，勢必也將成為外界持續關注的焦點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%B9%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E8%A2%AB%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B%E5%85%A8%E7%A8%8B%E8%A2%AB%E9%8C%84%E4%B8%8B-163713134.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2589%25B9%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25A8%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%258C%2584%25E4%25B8%258B-163713134.html&d=EcPZaEoD0XJ%2BoQ%2BnfGpsrcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=755d9fd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%B9%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E8%A2%AB%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B%E5%85%A8%E7%A8%8B%E8%A2%AB%E9%8C%84%E4%B8%8B-163713134.html</a>"},{"pid":"d98419efb00412f743d9a40d636e2f06223de8f6","tid":765694,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T05:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f9c15c5a94deeb80e19fe642009b7ba3698838","tid":765694,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T05:15:12.000Z","msg":"五毛進場未"},{"pid":"4c9fa393cf1245aa7fc2c02ee1c83fc74dadba94","tid":765694,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T05:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1ebc0c2085f3837859b83527d58da6c9a19fd1","tid":765694,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T05:19:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69d9bb2ef66bd6c5bd83548007cf9084c838163c","tid":765694,"uid":120852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T05:21:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做左84年人都唔化！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n響大陸批評習總真係嫌命長啦！<br />\n咪當提早上天堂囉！<br />\n走早幾年者！<br />\n<br />\n沒事兒沒事兒！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"da881a48fbe46244a24ed1e44b89b0797074e423","tid":765694,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c1ebc0c2085f3837859b83527d58da6c9a19fd1","tid":765694,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T05:19:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"落地獄就有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}